#NAPS image was used in this project,and 20 images was selected according to each of the 6 emotion categories,

##The image with the strongest female rating was selected for Women, 
and the image with the strongest male rating was selected for Men. 
No image appears twice. Ratings are on a 1-9 scale

##Neutral Images Baseline / Control (4 Images)
These images have all 6 emotion ratings below 2.5 genuinely flat effect. 
They are suitable as controls or resting baselines in a study.

##Gender-Divergent Images (4 Images)
These images are moderately low in overall emotion, 
but men and women rate them very differently making them scientifically interesting additions to the set.


